Grammar

Rule 0     S' -> program
Rule 1     program -> program global_statement
Rule 2     global_statement -> assignment
Rule 3     assignment -> ID POW_ASSIGN expression
Rule 4     expression -> STRING
Rule 5     function_definition -> DEF ID LPAREN parameter_list RPAREN COLON INDENT function_body DENT
Rule 6     program -> global_statement
Rule 7     global_statement -> function_definition
Rule 8     assignment -> ID INT_DIV_ASSIGN expression
Rule 9     expression -> FLOAT
Rule 10    function_statement -> assignment
Rule 11    function_body -> function_body function_statement
Rule 12    assignment -> ID PLUS_ASSIGN expression
Rule 13    expression -> INT
Rule 14    function_body -> function_statement
Rule 15    assignment -> ID MINUS_ASSIGN expression
Rule 16    expression -> ID
Rule 17    parameter_list -> <empty>
Rule 18    assignment -> ID MULT_ASSIGN expression
Rule 19    parameter_list -> parameter
Rule 20    assignment -> ID DIV_ASSIGN expression
Rule 21    parameter_list -> parameter_list COMMA parameter
Rule 22    assignment -> ID MOD_ASSIGN expression
Rule 23    parameter -> ID
Rule 24    assignment -> ID ASSIGN expression
Rule 25    parameter -> ID ASSIGN expression

